	<div class="txt">
			<div class="para">
				<p>
					Welcome to e-Voting! Where casting the votes has been made easy. Start the voting process by verifying if you have been authorized as a voter. 
				</p>
			</div>
			
				<a href="verify">VERIFY</a>
						
